{"tid":643434,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【影評】無劇透 《復仇者聯盟 3：無限之戰》IMAX 3D 觀後評 十年鋪排顛峰之作","createTime":"2018-04-26T13:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T14:42:41.000Z","uid":7103,"like":9,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"45798c7451e929fdecdb489deb635fc723394ba0","tid":643434,"uid":7103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:16:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/04/26/avengers-infinity-war-3/movie-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2Favengers-infinity-war-3%2Fmovie-2%2F&d=U%2F7c%2BUS8Ziu8fUlWKI0m3NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=0f4ca8bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/04/26/avengers-infinity-war-3/movie-2/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇<br />\n1時<br />\n超悶﹗等個2小時只有寧聲打鬥，一D都唔好笑，講D里語我地又唔明。或者係係未到個level, 但如果以好笑又唔及thor 3，打鬥場面亦唔夠勁。<br />\n<br />\n你話我膚淺都係咁講.....一個字，期望越大，失望越大.....老實講任何一套Marvel都好睇過佢，最後個彩蛋真係浪費時間咁等收場......又等多年拍下集.........就係似哈里波特咁，硬係要分上下集! 晒時間!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHKTIF<br />\n6時<br />\n呢集劇情係我睇過marvel系列裏面最爛既一套<br />\n你居然話係咪忠粉都值得入場， 真係唔知你係真傻定係喺度賣廣告"},{"pid":"689d34316a647319793955b31daccf25a9d27a4d","tid":643434,"uid":182286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:17:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a9ddd06225aa3c8c7c9e69996c924e399da9dc2","tid":643434,"uid":46498,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:22:17.000Z","msg":"呢套垃圾，唔好話神作Justice League ，連Suicide Squad都好睇過佢多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8c5b065415ed82753659b34937d8b06ca99fca","tid":643434,"uid":7103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:23:59.000Z","msg":"DC打手連業專影評嘅comment section都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb69d2d0743cfcc75301c759f4501a50927a26b","tid":643434,"uid":34572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0a9ddd06225aa3c8c7c9e699